      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ByteByteGo discusses 2 and 3\n\nSays 2 doesn't have a collision cause\nit combines the 4th approach with 2\n\nCompares with 3 saying UUID is\nrequired in 3 (hashing) while 2\ndoesn't require UUID",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ByteByteGo discusses 2 and 3\n\nSays 2 doesn't have a collision cause it combines the 4th approach with 2\n\nCompares with 3 saying UUID is required in 3 (hashing) while 2 doesn't require UUID",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
