    {
      "id": "5LUdsqYKljx_05Gww_0L3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2164.1290919099915,
      "y": 3172.008209270292,
      "width": 439.27312559316306,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0T",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1163336585,
      "version": 621,
      "versionNonce": 814633065,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782654546924,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "URL Genaration Service\n\nThis service handles all write\noperations. It validates incoming URLs,\ngenerates a unique short code, handles\nany custom alias the user provides, and\nstores metadata such as the expiry\ndate, creation time, and user ID. Since\nwrite traffic is relatively low\ncompared to reads, this service doesn’t\nneed to scale aggressively.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "URL Genaration Service\n\nThis service handles all write operations. It validates incoming URLs, generates a unique short code, handles any custom alias the user provides, and stores metadata such as the expiry date, creation time, and user ID. Since write traffic is relatively low compared to reads, this service doesn’t need to scale aggressively.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jCLwPS-g5u6HDTw4VZ7oV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2163.6016095682626,
      "y": 3522.17123754852,
      "width": 439.27312559316306,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0U",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 952466439,
      "version": 702,
      "versionNonce": 555375433,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782654546924,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Redirection Service\n\nThe Redirection Service handles the\noverwhelming majority of traffic,\ntypically billions of GET requests per\nday, so it must be fast, stateless, and\nhorizontally scalable.\n\nFor a given short code, it looks up the\noriginal long URL, checks that the link\nis still valid (not expired or\ndeleted), and issues an HTTP 301\n(permanent) or 302 (temporary) redirect\nbased on the system’s policy. It also\ncaches frequently accessed mappings to\nminimize database hits.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Redirection Service\n\nThe Redirection Service handles the overwhelming majority of traffic, typically billions of GET requests per day, so it must be fast, stateless, and horizontally scalable.\n\nFor a given short code, it looks up the original long URL, checks that the link is still valid (not expired or deleted), and issues an HTTP 301 (permanent) or 302 (temporary) redirect based on the system’s policy. It also caches frequently accessed mappings to minimize database hits.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kjLL-EwGgYE2J4AL_Yvmk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2926.7729085750893,
      "y": 3270.352846288709,
      "width": 269.2478942871094,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0V",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 493655047,
      "version": 519,
      "versionNonce": 1876820041,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782665736820,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "POST FLow (Write)",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "POST FLow (Write)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "eWEoJzsuQOiswVUFx2f5C",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2934.306952057799,
      "y": 3338.864573857132,
      "width": 814,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0W",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 921336615,
      "version": 1074,
      "versionNonce": 1210111177,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782654170435,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Client sends a POST /api/v1/shorten request with the long URL.\nThe Load Balancer routes the request to a URL Shortening Service instance.\nThe service validates the URL format and generates a unique short code.\nThe service stores the mapping (short_code -> long_url) in the Database.\nThe service returns the complete short URL to the client.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Client sends a POST /api/v1/shorten request with the long URL.\nThe Load Balancer routes the request to a URL Shortening Service instance.\nThe service validates the URL format and generates a unique short code.\nThe service stores the mapping (short_code -> long_url) in the Database.\nThe service returns the complete short URL to the client.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "gXWh5iiJNKXaq13RlFQ-9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2943.163842784579,
      "y": 3578.524706901232,
      "width": 250.26388549804688,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0r",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 370390215,
      "version": 732,
      "versionNonce": 1605932585,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782665740888,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "GET FLow (Read)",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GET FLow (Read)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZNvlpZKH8_SP8Z6E6LXsP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2937.687480285505,
      "y": 3663.261031189832,
      "width": 739.7941382607914,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0s",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2003796967,
      "version": 1428,
      "versionNonce": 516473511,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782654209277,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Client requests GET /abc123.\nThe Load Balancer routes to a Redirection Service instance.\nThe service first checks the Redis Cache for the short code.\nOn cache hit, return the long URL immediately.\nOn cache miss, query the Database, then populate the cache.\nThe service validates the link is not expired.\nReturn an HTTP 302 redirect to the original URL.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Client requests GET /abc123.\nThe Load Balancer routes to a Redirection Service instance.\nThe service first checks the Redis Cache for the short code.\nOn cache hit, return the long URL immediately.\nOn cache miss, query the Database, then populate the cache.\nThe service validates the link is not expired.\nReturn an HTTP 302 redirect to the original URL.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
