      "text": "-read through\n-LRU Cache\n\nkey : shortCode\nvalue : longUrl",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "-read through\n-LRU Cache\n\nkey : shortCode\nvalue : longUrl",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tCMtF7z5qb2KOkJl6w1kw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2159.982235623117,
      "y": 4004.3157986583365,
      "width": 610.7673651285089,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1c",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 372637607,
      "version": 232,
      "versionNonce": 2107771433,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782654546924,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cache\n\nTo achieve sub-50ms latency at 35,000 QPS, we need a\ndistributed cache. It stores frequently accessed URL\nmappings, which reduces database load for popular links\nand provides sub-millisecond lookup times.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cache\n\nTo achieve sub-50ms latency at 35,000 QPS, we need a distributed cache. It stores frequently accessed URL mappings, which reduces database load for popular links and provides sub-millisecond lookup times.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uOdY-mOt6x0Y8fhXbyuHO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 613.3278715435816,
      "y": 3820.218452810497,
      "width": 215.59991455078125,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
