    {
      "id": "lOE3Exi1FWhHgmKMHBfUk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 632.4305106806446,
      "y": 4173.45086360266,
      "width": 528,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1o",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1906583881,
      "version": 667,
      "versionNonce": 203051399,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782666048061,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "URLs -> 10M per day (Write)\n100:1 Read to Write ~ 1 billion redirects (Read)\n\nWrite QPS = 10,000,000 / 24*3600 ~ 115 QPS\nPeak factor = 3 ~ 350 QPS\n\nRead QPS = 1,000,000,000/24*3600 ~ 11500 QPS\nPeak Factor = 3 ~ 35000 QPS\n\nURLs 10M/day * 365 days = 3.65 billion/yr\n\nStorage per year = 3.65B * 300 bytes ~ 1.1TB/yr\nFor 5 years = 5.5TB\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "URLs -> 10M per day (Write)\n100:1 Read to Write ~ 1 billion redirects (Read)\n\nWrite QPS = 10,000,000 / 24*3600 ~ 115 QPS\nPeak factor = 3 ~ 350 QPS\n\nRead QPS = 1,000,000,000/24*3600 ~ 11500 QPS\nPeak Factor = 3 ~ 35000 QPS\n\nURLs 10M/day * 365 days = 3.65 billion/yr\n\nStorage per year = 3.65B * 300 bytes ~ 1.1TB/yr\nFor 5 years = 5.5TB\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Y2L7hZkFqBYM1aGDBJlqI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1304.4313682510733,
      "y": 4210.9819267814955,
      "width": 474.2959812084368,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 176213799,
      "version": 521,
      "versionNonce": 229039529,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782666174263,
      "link": null,
      "text": "Design Notes\n\n- Short key generation using Base62\n- Alphabet: a-z, A-Z, 0-9 (62 chars)\n- 6^62 or 7^62\n- 6 chars gives ~56B combinations; 7 chars\ngives ~3.5T unique codes",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 0,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b1q",
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design Notes\n\n- Short key generation using Base62\n- Alphabet: a-z, A-Z, 0-9 (62 chars)\n- 6^62 or 7^62\n- 6 chars gives ~56B combinations; 7 chars gives ~3.5T unique codes",
      "autoResize": false
    }
  ],
